{
  "stem": "14156.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I laid up there and put my-- my back towards the thing-- towards the-- you know-- and nobody bothered me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I didn't have to go through whatever happened down-- down below.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That only lasted a few days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one morning, I said-- [LAUGHS] I look up-- I wake up, I look down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody's gone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, wow, what's going on?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I go down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I ran to the gate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And here, there was about three, four German soldiers laying there, dead.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the jeep stood there, with Americans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think it was the Eighth Army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they waved to me-- come on, come on!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Get out!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I seen-- that's it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I did kiss the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Really.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, from there, I walked out of the camp, out of this-- it wasn't in the woods.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I come to a highway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Across the highway was a train station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was a big corrugated-- corrugated place with-- no, they call that a depot.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, from merchandise, to put in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And two or three MPs standing in front of it, with their guns and let-- would let-- would let nobody in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the people outside, the-- the-- the haftlinge-- you know, the-- the-- the prisoners-- pleaded-- please, please, let us in, let us in!",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they knew-- the-- the MP knew what was inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was piled up with sugar.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Finally, they opened the thing up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And everybody just ran in there, ripped open the sugar, and, with their hands, and ate the thing, without thinking-- anything.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And also there was a cereal in there, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I looked at it, and I-- I don't know, my brain was still working.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I went in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
